## Overview

The **Kabuto (Samurai Helmet)** is one of the most famous **traditional origami models**.\
It represents the helmet worn by Japanese samurai warriors and is often folded during celebrations related to strength, courage, and protection.

This model is simple, geometric, and iconic, making it a **great beginner project** while still carrying strong cultural symbolism.

