## Recommended Paper

This model works well with larger sheets because it can actually be **worn like a hat**.

Suggested sizes:

- **20 × 20 cm** (small decorative model)
- **30 × 30 cm** (large display model)
- **Newspaper sheet** (traditional children's activity in Japan)
